# Phase 4 — Cutover diff reports (contain PII like sales_person_name).
# Production runs from the workspace root; tests run from a sub-crate's cwd
# (e.g. `service_impl/`), so the same relative path resolves under multiple
# locations. The `**/` glob covers both, with the .gitkeep escape clause
# preserving the canonical empty directory at the workspace root.
**/.planning/migration-backup/*.json
!.planning/migration-backup/.gitkeep
